response.original_title: Darkwing Duck. His favorite adventures: Justice Ducks Unite!
response.overview: Not one, not two, but a Fearsome Five of Darkwing Duck's most dastardly enemies - Negaduck, Quackerjack, Bushroot, Megavolt and Liquidator - have taken over St. Canard! Not it's up to Darkwing to lead the mighty Justice Ducks - Gizmoduck, Neptunia, Stegmutt and Morgana McCawber - in the battle of the century to liberate the city! Get ready for some furious feather-flying fun as the daring and dapper Darkwing Duck faces his toughest challenge yet!
response.title: Darkwing Duck. His favorite adventures: Justice Ducks Unite!
